Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,# Queen of Misfits 錯位女王
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,## 前奏
Comment: 0,0:00:12.14,0:00:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,## 主歌-1
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.04,0:00:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}噢，多麼心痛\NOh, it's murder
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.33,0:00:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}當你又用沒事般的口氣訓我\Nthe way you tell me off like it's alright
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.83,0:00:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}即使你如何難過\Nand even at your worst
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.29,0:00:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}仍給我力氣繼續\Nyou strengthen my will to fight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.71,0:00:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你不知道你看上了什麼貨色\NAnd you don't know what you're getting into
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我回到家裡最是舒服\NI'm feeling right right at home
Comment: 0,0:00:33.01,0:00:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,## 副歌-B
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.91,0:00:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我就是錯位女王\N'Cause I'm the queen of misfits
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.61,0:00:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}是你的夢中情人\NI'm the stuff of your dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.06,0:00:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我是自己導演\N'Cause I declare who I am
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.69,0:00:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}眼見不就為真\NEverything's not as seems
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.08,0:00:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我要對你施魔咒\NI'm gonna put a spell on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.53,0:00:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不管你接不接受\Nand it's a dazzling truth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.28,0:00:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我會自己找到路\NAnd I can find my way
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.34,0:00:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你的存在無所謂\Nwith or without you
Comment: 0,0:00:53.33,0:00:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,## 導歌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.43,0:00:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}給我聽好\NSo hear our call
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.18,0:01:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我們要變得家喻戶曉\NWe're tryna make a name for ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.28,0:01:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你們曾有機會能跟我\NThere was a chance that you and I
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.13,0:01:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}跟我和好\Nwould be ok
