Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}現在看看我們\NTake a look at us now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.38,0:01:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}抹掉剛剛的淚水\Nhad to cry for a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.83,0:02:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}又回到了最佳狀態\Nbut now we're back on our best
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.38,0:02:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}即使看到罪過投影\Nwhile you projected the sin
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.84,0:02:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我們在這曾如火燒\NThere was hell for us here before
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.63,0:02:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}現在有差多少？\Nwhat's the difference from now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.96,0:02:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我們得自己找出路\NWe had to try and find our way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我們迷路，卻又被找到\NWe were lost but then were found
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.03,0:02:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我們心裡都有個壞人\NAnd there's a villain in all of us
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.76,0:02:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不過是要個朋友\Nstill needed a friend
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.03,0:02:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}每分每秒都是機會\NWhen every moment's a chance for us
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}來償還以前罪行\Nto make all our amends
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.18,0:02:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}這從一開始就很困難\NAnd it's hard since the start of it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.98,0:02:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}從來就沒簡單過\NIt's never been easy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.26,0:02:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你以為我們失去的魔法\NAnd the magic you thought we'd lost
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.68,0:02:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我們靠彼此找回來\NIt took ourselves while you turned away
